\id 2TH - Minimib dialect (Kalam) NT [kmhM] -Papua New Guinea 2008 (web version -2012 bd) 
\h 2 Tesalonaika 
\toc1 Pol mɨj kɨsen nɨb ak Tesalonaika bin bɨ kɨrop ñu kɨl tɨkak 
\toc2 2 Tesalonaika 
\toc3 2Te 
\mt1 2 Tesalonaika  
\mt2 Pol mɨj kɨsen nɨb ak Tesalonaika bin bɨ kɨrop ñu kɨl tɨkak  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Cɨn Pol, Sailas, Timoti, nɨbep Bapi cɨn God Bɨ Kɨb Jisas Krais apɨl mal bin bɨ kɨri taun kɨb Tesalonaika mɨdebɨm okok, mɨj nɨbaul ñu kɨl tɨkobɨn.   
\p
\v 2 God Bapi cɨn abe, Bɨ Kɨb Jisas Krais abe, nɨbep mapɨn nɨŋɨl dɨ tep ger, nɨbi mɨdmagɨl nab nɨbi adaŋ kapkap mɨd tep gɨnɨmɨb.   
\s1 Krais apek, God ne bin bɨ okok kɨrop mɨnɨm kɨb agnɨgab  
\p
\v 3 Pen ai mam sɨkop. Nɨbi ned Krais nɨŋ dölɨgɨpɨm rek mer; nɨbi ned pen pen mɨdmagɨl lölɨgɨpɨm rek mer; mɨñi nɨbi kɨlɨs gɨl Krais nop nɨŋ dɨ kɨlɨs gɨl, nɨbi magɨlsek Krais bin bɨ ai mam okok pen pen mɨdmagɨl lɨpɨm ak nɨŋɨl, cɨn per nep God nop tep agɨn.  
\v 4 Krais bin bɨ ne mɨdem, bin bɨ ognap nɨbep gɨ tɨmel gel, mɨker apek koslam mɨdebɨm ak pen gos par ma nɨŋɨl, Krais nop nɨŋ dɨ kɨlɨs gɨl cɨg tep yɨb gɨpɨm. Nɨb ak, cɨn God cöc ne karɨp lɨm ke ke okok amɨl, Krais mɨnɨm tep ag ñɨ ajɨl, per nep nɨbi nɨg gɨpɨm ak kɨrop ag ñɨbɨn.  
\v 5 Nɨb ak cɨn nɨpɨn, God ne mɨnɨm tɨg bɨlok tep gɨp nɨŋɨl ne agek nɨbi God karɨp lɨm seb kab ar alaŋ sɨŋak am mɨdenɨgabɨm. Mɨñi pen mɨnɨm tep nɨbak agem nɨbep gɨ tɨmel gel mɨker dɨlɨg gɨ mɨdebɨm.  
\v 6 God ne mɨnɨm tɨg bɨlok tep gɨp rek, bin bɨ nɨbep mɨker ñɨbal okok kɨrop pen ak rek nep mɨker ñɨnɨgab.  
\v 7 Pen nɨbi bin bɨ mɨker dɨlɨg gɨ mɨdebɨm okok, God nɨbep abe cɨnop abe dɨ tep gɨnɨgab. Bɨ Kɨb Jisas seb kab ar alaŋ nɨb ejol kɨlɨs ne okok poŋ dɨl, mab mɨlaŋ rek yɨnek nɨŋlɨg gɨ mɨseŋ onɨgab ñɨn nɨbak nep God ne nɨg gɨnɨgab.  
\v 8 Bin bɨ God nop gos ma nɨŋɨl, Bɨ Kɨb cɨn Jisas mɨnɨm tep ne ak nɨŋɨl, ageb rek ma gɨpal bin bɨ okok kɨrop pen yur ñɨnɨgab.  
\v 9 Bin bɨ nɨb okok, Bɨ Kɨb karɨp lɨm tep ne kɨlɨs sek melɨk sek mɨdenɨgab seb kab ar alaŋ sɨŋak amnɨmel rek ma lɨnɨgab; per mɨs ken mɨdɨl yur kɨb dɨlɨg gɨ mɨdenɨgal.  
\v 10 Bɨ Kɨb apek, bin bɨ sɨŋ ne yɨb nop agel ar amnɨgab; bin bɨ nop nɨŋ dɨpal okok, nop nɨŋɨl kɨb gaul gɨnɨgal. Pen Krais mɨnɨm tep nɨbep ag ñɨnok nɨŋ dɨpek rek, nɨbi ke abe nɨb aknɨb rek nep gɨnɨgabɨm.   
\p
\v 11 Ar nɨbak nep, nɨbep gos nɨŋɨl God nop per sobok gɨl apɨn, “Tesalonaika bin bɨ okok bin bɨ nak ke dɨpan rek, kɨlɨs nak gek kɨri bin bɨ nak ke gɨpal rek gɨnɨmel; kɨlɨs nak gek kɨri gɨ tep gɨn ag gos nɨpal ar ak, nɨb aknɨb rek nep gɨnɨmel; Krais bin bɨ ne mɨdɨl, ne ageb rek nep gɨn, ag gos nɨpal ak, kɨlɨs nak gek nɨg aknɨb rek nep gɨnɨmel,” apɨn.  
\v 12 God Bɨ Kɨb Jisas Krais kɨri apɨl mal nɨbep mapɨn nɨŋɨl dɨ tep gɨpir rek, nɨbi gɨ tep nep gɨlɨg gɨ mɨdem nɨŋlɨg gɨ, bin bɨ okok nɨŋɨl Bɨ Kɨb cɨn Jisas Krais bɨ melɨk tep ke sek mɨdeb ak nɨŋnɨgal. Pen nɨbi Jisas Krais bin bɨ ne mɨdebɨm rek, melɨk tep ke ne nɨbak nɨbep abe pak ñɨnɨgab. Nɨg gɨnɨmɨŋ, agɨl, God nop sobok gɨpɨn.   
\c 2  
\s1 Bɨ tɨmel ak  
\p
\v 1 Ai mam sɨkop. Bɨ Kɨb cɨn Jisas Krais adɨk gɨ apɨl cɨnop yɨprɨg dek ne eip mɨdonɨgabɨn mɨnɨm ak agnɨgain.  
\v 2 Pen bin bɨ ognap agebal, Bɨ Kɨb adɨk gɨ onɨgab ñɨn ak pɨs nep owɨp agebal. Pen mɨnɨm tom agɨl, Pol bɨ okok God Kaun gos ñek mɨnɨm aglak ak nɨŋɨl nɨbep agobɨn, agenɨmel, aka mɨnɨm tom agɨl, Pol bɨ okok nɨb agel bɨ ognap nɨŋɨl mɨnɨm dopal ak nɨŋɨl nɨbep agobɨn, agenɨmel, aka mɨnɨm tom agɨl, Pol bɨ okok mɨj ñu kɨl tɨkɨl yokel owɨp ak nɨŋɨl nɨbep agobɨn, agenɨmel ak, mɨdmagɨl nɨbi pɨlɨs gek, Pol bɨ okok kɨri ke mɨnɨm nɨbaul ag yokpal agɨl gos par ma nɨŋnɨmɨb.  
\v 3 Pen nɨŋ tep gɨnɨmɨb. Bin bɨ ognap nɨbep mɨnɨm esek agenɨmel, mɨnɨm kɨri ak ma dɨnɨmɨb. Bɨ Kɨb adɨk gɨ onɨgab ñɨn ak kɨsen onɨgab. Pen ned ak, bin bɨ koŋai nep God nop kɨrɨg gɨl, gos kɨri ke kɨsen gɨl abramek gɨnɨgal. Nɨg gel nɨŋlɨg gɨ, God nop kaual maual mɨdeb bɨ ak mɨseŋ lek bin bɨ nop nɨŋnɨgal. Pen kɨsen Bɨ Tɨmel yɨb nɨbak mab ke eyaŋ amnɨgab.  
\v 4 Bɨ Tɨmel nɨbak tap tari tari yɨb god apal okok abe, tap tari tari sobok gɨpal okok abe ag sɨkol gɨl, yɨb ne ke nep agek ar amnɨgab. Ne am God sobok gep karɨp ak am bɨsɨg gɨl, yad me God, agnɨgab.   
\p
\v 5 Nɨbep eip mɨdɨl, nɨg gɨnɨgab agɨl agnek ak pen saköl gɨpɨm rek lɨp.  
\v 6 Nɨbi nɨpɨm, tap alap Bɨ Tɨmel kanɨb komɨb ak me, mɨñi nɨg gɨnɨmɨŋ rek ma lɨp. God ne ke ag lak ñɨn ak nep nɨg gɨnɨgab.   
\p
\v 7 Pen mɨñi ñɨn aul, God nop kaual maual mɨdeb bɨ ak apek, gɨnɨgal ar ak bɨr gɨpal ak pen sɨkol nep gɨpal; gɨ kɨb gɨplap pen bɨ kanɨb komɨb bɨ nɨbak mɨdek nɨŋlɨg gɨ, God nop kaual maual mɨdeb bɨ ak, bin bɨ okok tapɨn lɨp gɨ kɨd ne okok dad amnɨmɨŋ rek ma lɨp. Nɨb ak, tap si tap tɨmel sɨkol rek gɨ dam dapɨl gel nɨŋlɨg gɨ, God gek bɨ kanɨb komɨb ak ke okok amnɨgab.  
\v 8 God gek bɨ kanɨb komɨb ak ke okok amnɨgab ak, God nop kaual maual mɨdeb bɨ ak mɨseŋ lɨnɨgab. Pen Bɨ Kɨb Jisas onɨgab ñɨn nɨbak, ne tɨb kadɨg gɨl apɨl mɨnɨm nep agek, Bɨ Tɨmel ak pɨs nep ap yap paknɨgab.  
\v 9 God nop kaual maual mɨdeb bɨ onɨgab ak, ne Seten kɨlɨs ne magɨlsek dɨl, esek agɨl, tap ma gep ke ke koŋai yɨb nep, tap nɨŋeb ma nɨŋeb ke ke koŋai yɨb nep gɨ dam mɨdek nɨŋlɨg gɨ, bin bɨ kɨb gaul gɨnɨgal.  
\v 10 God nop kaual maual mɨdeb bɨ ak, bin bɨ okok kɨrop esek agɨl, neb neb gɨl, lɨp lɨp gɨl gɨ dam mɨdek nɨŋlɨg gɨ, mab ke eyaŋ amnɨg gɨnɨgal bin bɨ okok mɨnɨm ne ak dɨnɨgal. Kɨri Krais mɨnɨm tep ak nɨŋɨl mɨnɨm nɨŋɨd agɨl nɨŋ dɨl mɨdmagɨl nab kɨri adaŋ lɨplap ak, God kɨrop bin bɨ ne ke rek dɨpkop. Pen kɨri nɨg ma gɨnɨgal; kɨri mɨnɨm tep ak yo nɨŋnɨgal.  
\v 11-12 Tari gɨnɨg: Krais mɨnɨm nɨŋɨd ak ma dɨl, tap si tap tɨmel gɨl mɨñ mɨñ gɨnɨgal. Nɨb ak, God gek kɨri magɨlsek mɨnɨm tom nɨbak tapɨn nɨŋ dɨnɨgal nɨŋɨl ne kɨrop mɨnɨm kɨb agɨl mab ke eyaŋ ag yoknɨgab.   
\p
\v 13 Pen nɨbep ai mam Bɨ Kɨb mɨdmagɨl lɨp okok gos nɨŋɨl, per nep God nop tep agɨn. Tari gɨnɨg: bɨrarɨk ped okok God gos ne ke nɨŋɨl agak, bin bɨ okok mɨnɨm tep yad ak nɨŋ del, Kaun yad kaun kɨri nab adaŋ mɨdɨl gos tep ñek kɨri bin bɨ sɨŋ mɨdel nɨŋlɨg gɨ, yad kɨrop bin bɨ yad ke dɨnɨgain, agak. God ne nɨb agak ak, nɨbep nep nɨŋɨl ag lak.   
\p
\v 14 Cɨn Krais mɨnɨm tep nɨbep ag ñɨnok nɨŋlɨg gɨ, tap tep agebin nɨbaul God ne ke nɨbep ñɨnɨgain agak. God gak nɨbak, Bɨ Kɨb cɨn Jisas Krais melɨk tep aknɨb ke sek mɨdeb ak, nɨbi ne eip mɨdɨl melɨk tep ne nɨbak ognap dɨl mɨñ mɨñ gɨlɨg gɨ mɨdenɨgabɨm, agɨl gak.  
\v 15 Nɨb ak me, ai mam sɨkop, Bɨ Kɨb Jisas Krais eip mɨd tep gɨnɨgabɨn, agɨl, kɨlɨs gɨl, mɨnɨm nɨbep ag ñɨnok nɨpek ak abe, mɨnɨm ñu kɨl tɨkɨl agnok nɨpek ak abe nɨŋ dɨ kɨlɨs gɨl mɨdenɨmɨb.   
\p
\v 16 Bapi God cɨnop mɨdmagɨl lɨl dɨ tep yɨb gek tap tep dɨnɨgabɨn agɨl gos sek mɨdobɨn. Bapi God abe, Bɨ Kɨb cɨn Jisas Krais ne ke abe,  
\v 17 apɨl mal nɨbep kod mɨder, gos sek mɨdɨl, wög kɨri apɨl mal ak ma kɨrɨg gɨl, mɨnɨm tep kɨri ak ag ñɨl, gɨ tep gɨlɨg gɨ nep mɨdenɨmɨb.   
\c 3  
\s1 Cɨnop gos nɨŋɨl, God nop sobok gɨnɨmɨb  
\p
\v 1 Pen ai mam sɨkop, mɨnɨm nokɨm alap mɨdeb. Cɨnop God nop sobok gɨlɨg gɨ mɨdenɨmɨb. Nɨbep Bɨ Kɨb mɨnɨm tep ag ñɨnok nɨŋ dɨpek, bin bɨ nɨbi ognap nɨbep nɨŋɨl Bɨ Kɨb mɨnɨm tep ak rek nep nɨŋ del, bin bɨ ognap koŋai nep kɨd kɨd okok mɨnɨm tep ak nɨŋɨl, Bɨ Kɨb mɨnɨm tep ne ke nep mɨdeb ak agɨl nɨŋ dɨlak. Nɨb ak, God nop ag nɨŋɨl, Bɨ Kɨb mɨnɨm tep ak bin bɨ karɨp lɨm nab sɨŋaul mɨdebal kɨrop ag ñon, ned nɨbep nab sɨŋak gak rek, nɨb aknɨb rek nep gɨnɨmɨŋ.  
\v 2 Pen God nop sobok gɨl tap alap ag nɨŋnɨmɨb. God ne gek bɨ tɨmel tap si tap tɨmel nep gɨpal okok, cɨnop tap alap gɨnɨmel rek ma lɨnɨmɨŋ. Tari gɨnɨg: bin bɨ ognap Krais mɨnɨm tep ak ma nɨŋ dɨpal.   
\p
\v 3 Pen Bɨ Kɨb agɨp rek, per nep aknɨb rek nep gɨp. Ne nɨbep gek nɨbi mɨnɨm ne nɨŋ dɨ wös gɨl nop cɨg dɨ wös gɨl gɨ mɨdem, Seten nɨbep lɨp gɨ tɨmel gɨnɨmɨŋ rek ma lɨnɨgab.  
\v 4 Pen Bɨ Kɨb cɨnop gos ñek gos sek mɨdɨl nɨpɨn, mɨnɨm nɨbep ag ñɨnok ak, nɨbi dɨl nɨb aknɨb rek nep gɨlɨg gɨ mɨdenɨgabɨm.  
\v 5 Bɨ Kɨb nop sobok gɨl agobɨn, ne nɨbep gos tep ñek, God bin bɨ mɨdmagɨl lɨp rek nɨŋɨl, Krais yur kɨb dak pen kɨlɨs gɨl tap tari nop gɨnɨg gak ak ma kɨrɨg gak ak nɨŋɨl, nɨg aknɨb rek nep gɨnɨgabɨm.   
\s1 Wög gɨl nep tap ñɨŋnɨgabɨm  
\p
\v 6 Ai mam sɨkop. Bɨ Kɨb Jisas Krais mɨnɨm yad bin bɨ okok ag ñɨnɨmɨb ag lak rek nɨbep agobɨn. Mam ognap wög ma gɨl yokop nep gɨ ajɨl, apɨn rek ma genɨmel, kɨrop eip mɨnɨm mɨnɨm ma agnɨmɨb.  
\v 7 Nɨbi ke nɨpɨm, cɨn nɨbep eip kɨn mɨdɨl golɨgɨpɨn ar ak gɨnɨgabɨm, Bɨ Kɨb nop tep gɨnɨgab. Cɨn yokop ma mɨdolɨgɨpɨn.  
\v 8 Bin bɨ ognap tap magɨl kɨri yokop ma dɨ ñɨŋɨn, agɨl, pɨb nab kɨslɨm eyaŋ tɨpɨk yur gɨl nep tap ñɨbolɨgɨpɨn.  
\v 9 God wög gɨpɨn rek, nɨbep ag nɨŋɨl tap abramek dɨl ñɨbnop ak pen nɨbep nag tep ar ak yomon nɨŋɨl nɨg aknɨb rek nep gɨnɨmɨb, agɨl, ke tɨpɨk yur gɨl tap ñɨbolɨgɨpɨn.  
\v 10 Pen nɨbep eip mɨdɨl agolɨgɨpɨn, “Bin bɨ wög ma gɨnɨmel okok tap ma ñɨŋnɨmel,” agolɨgɨpɨn ak nɨpɨm.   
\p
\v 11 Mɨnɨm alap nɨpɨn ak, bin bɨ nɨbi ognap wög ma gɨl, yokop nep mɨdɨl, tɨgoŋ tɨgoŋ gɨ ajɨl, mɨnɨm pɨg kɨlopɨl agɨl, bin bɨ okok nɨg gɨpal nɨg gɨpal apal.  
\v 12 Bɨ Kɨb Jisas Krais nop wög gɨpɨn rek, bin bɨ nɨb okok kɨrop mɨnɨm kɨlɨs agɨl agobɨn, kapkap mɨd tep gɨl, wög ke gɨl tap ñɨŋnɨmɨb.   
\p
\v 13 Pen ai mam sɨkop. Nɨbi nag tep ar ak nep gɨ damɨl, yɨrɨk marɨk gonɨmɨŋ, tap tari tap tep nɨpɨm ak nep kɨlɨs gɨlɨg gɨ nep mɨdenɨmɨb.   
\p
\v 14 Mɨnɨm mɨj ñu kɨl tɨkɨl agobɨn aul, bin bɨ ognap ma nɨŋenɨmel, bin bɨ an an nɨb gɨpal ak nɨŋ tep gɨl, kɨrop mɨnɨm mɨnɨm ma agnɨmɨb; yokop mɨdem kɨrop nabɨŋ gɨnɨmɨŋ.  
\v 15 Pen kɨrop kaual maual rek ma nɨŋnɨmɨb; mam cɨn agɨl ag ñɨ tep gɨnɨmɨb.   
\s1 Pol, “Nɨbi mɨdebɨm?” agɨp  
\p
\v 16 Bɨ Kɨb cɨnop gek gos par ma nɨpɨn ak, ne ke nɨbep magɨlsek eip mɨdek, nɨbi per nep tap tari tari gɨnɨgabɨm ak, mɨd tep gɨl gos par ma nɨŋnɨgabɨm.   
\p
\v 17 Yad Pol. Mɨnɨm dai aul ñɨnmagɨl yad ke ñu kɨl tɨkɨl, “Nɨbi mɨdebɨm?” agebin. Ñɨnmagɨl yad ke mɨnɨm ñu kɨl tɨkebin ak, per nɨb aul rek nep ñu kɨl tɨkpin ak me, nɨŋnɨgabɨm.  
\v 18 Bɨ Kɨb cɨn Jisas Krais nɨbep magɨlsek yɨmɨg nɨŋɨl, dɨ tep gɨlɨg gɨ mɨdonɨmɨŋ.   